Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.03,0:26:05.79,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H1C1B1B&}像堅毅盛開的花朵一般
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.53,0:26:16.49,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H1C1B1B&}無論何時都用盡全力去活着
